{"tid":1292084,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾賤種朗真正實力數據 update 20190707","createTime":"2019-07-07T06:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T04:19:36.000Z","uid":54373,"like":7,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a91c309a773c13dc24fce4d50c508162781cf0db","tid":1292084,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T06:57:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自己加返<br />\n<br />\n美斯入2球場波開始無計<br />\n<br />\n美斯 53 : 31 垃圾<br />\n<br />\n加返美斯射19球，都超20%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">垃圾賤種朗 已經玩完 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲比美斯拋離22球<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>歐洲金靴獎 賤朗21球 美斯36球 (拋離15球)<br />\n賤朗盃(朗迷話) 賤朗6球 美斯12球 (拋離6球)</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本週<br />\n賤種朗 - 3射0入<br />\n美斯 - 5射2入<br />\n<br />\n#數據post目的係唔想班<span style=\"color: red;\">賤朗迷再呃人</span><br />\n#上述數據由今季第1場比賽開始計算<br />\n#上述數據根據 who scored + 7m 賽後數據 每場累積而來<br />\n<br />\n賤種朗<br />\n聯賽: 177射21入球 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>(5球靠12碼)</strong></span> (11.8%)<br />\n歐聯: 47射6入球 1紅牌 (1球靠12碼) (12.7%)  <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">(8弟出局)</span></strong><br />\n意大利社區盾 6射1入 (16.6%)<br />\n意大利盃: n射0入<span style=\"color: red;\"> (0%入球率 意盃8郎已修業)</span><br />\n(190113vs 榜尾博洛尼亞, 官方沒有數據)<br />\n(190131vs 中游阿特蘭大, 官方沒有數據)<br />\n國際賽: 11射0入 (0%) <br />\n<strong><br />\n已射241球 得個28個入球 合共11.6%<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美斯<br />\n聯賽: 166射36入球 (4球靠12碼) (21.6%)<br />\n歐聯: 53射12入球 0紅牌 (22.6%) (1球12碼)<br />\n西班牙盃: n射2入<br />\n(190118vs 中游利雲特入1, 官方沒有數據)<br />\n(190131vs 強隊西維爾入1, 官方沒有數據)<br />\n(190227vs 死敵皇馬,0射0入)<br />\n國際賽: 4射0入 (0%) <br />\n<br />\n<strong>已223射入50球 合共22.4%</strong></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4b2607082773e3e1af57251ab1477c75bfae72d0","tid":1292084,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T06:58:04.000Z","msg":"入球率贏垃圾接近1倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17e79e385db826780e90e5c837764baed75ecbb4","tid":1292084,"uid":15830,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T06:58:53.000Z","msg":"數據王美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7567826339cc274b57849759793cae4b590a2d4","tid":1292084,"uid":54373,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"17e79e385db826780e90e5c837764baed75ecbb4","tid":1292084,"uid":15830,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T06:58:53.000Z","msg":"數據王美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:04:25.000Z","msg":"c朗帶領葡萄牙？<br />\n<br />\n拎過mvp未"},{"pid":"e4def13473148161942dc5f0495a4a6ff86cb1b4","tid":1292084,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ea346f8e7dca69290b53f29913e0abc75629f5","tid":1292084,"uid":23779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:58:50.000Z","msg":"真朗迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff180d318ebe60e9a4de6b057dec3de5c45f49ed","tid":1292084,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:06:46.000Z","msg":"朗迷又消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\"